{"tid":1738223,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【行動方針】黎明行動 黃昏歸家","createTime":"2019-11-19T07:31:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T15:20:21.000Z","uid":167548,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"929c6eabe4d4558850276b3eda2daacf6270f7ff","tid":1738223,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T07:31:51.000Z","msg":"BE WATER<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好再被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共用緊慢性天安門式鎮壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\npopo式鳩拉鎮壓/暗殺將成主調<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地是唔是要認清一個事實,<br />\n就是我方嘅抗爭武力靠實彈/車攻已可鎮壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n土共唔需要出老解去攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nThomas Tang : 攬炒  我們都錯了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1738165\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1738165</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n攬炒沒錯！但是我地沒能力逼佢地出老解！<br />\nor 運動鄧小強嘅鎮壓已足夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n解決方法：<br />\n星期一至五 黎明出動 <span style=\"color: red;\">收市前回家！</span><br />\n夜晚損耗太多, 港豬訓曬覺, 嬲完就繼續返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n星期六日：善用制度拎不反！<br />\n若無則不強求, 當做休息日！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">不被捕 不陣地</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"c23592fdf543cd83576e49cba8cdb3c00b08eb94","tid":1738223,"uid":338636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T07:33:00.000Z","msg":"[正能量撚]出去之前，希望你可以睇下呢個po<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1734559\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1734559</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>全個連登都係負能量，我要你地有正能量啊</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"43d03c285e7091c9cdce9abd6f03dd